org.apache.flink.api.common.serialization

类 TypeInformationSerializationSchema<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.common.serialization.TypeInformationSerializationSchema<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - The type to be serialized.
    所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, DeserializationSchema<T>, SerializationSchema<T>, ResultTypeQueryable<T>
    直接已知子类:
    TypeInformationSerializationSchema

    @Public
public class TypeInformationSerializationSchema<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements DeserializationSchema<T>, SerializationSchema<T>
    A serialization and deserialization schema that uses Flink's serialization stack to transform typed from and to byte arrays.
    另请参阅:

      • typeInfo

        private transient TypeInformation<T> typeInfo
        The type information, to be returned by getProducedType(). It is transient, because it is not serializable. Note that this means that the type information is not available at runtime, but only prior to the first serialization / deserialization.
